Mail URL Rewriter (MURLR)

MURLR is a Mail.app plugin which processes URLs you click on before passing it to the OS.  For example, if you have a URL which looks like
  

USAGE
* When you install MURLR, a preference panel appears in your Mail.app.
A URL rewrite rule is composed of three properties.
  Match regular expression will match against the entire URL

